Tusind tak!  I am trying to learn Danish, so it's great to find something in Danish with English subtitles.  Ditto for English stuff with Danish subtitles.

It's hard to learn here in the U.S. where no one speaks Danish except for the people in class with you, who speak it as badly as you do.
I wonder why you have chosen to study Danish in US?!
